**Simple Microservices App**
----------------------------
Both Apps must be running simultaneously
Install Sql Script and execute both files for user and items.
Import Postman collections and run all APIs.


**Note for Testing**
--------------------
In Security service when you run test for creating new user you must use these credentials(Email,Password) in @BeforeEach void method as it will login and generate JWT before any Test.
You must use both(Email,Password) in todo service and make sure you use the right id of item you run test for getItem,updateItem and deleteItem.
